parkinggarage.model

Class Garage

  • java.lang.Object
    • parkinggarage.model.Garage

  • public class Garage
extends java.lang.Object
    This Garage Class contains all information and logic for the Cars in the Garage. It keeps track of the cars in the garage and has logic for entering and exiting the garage Created by melle on 28-1-2017.
